{
  "name": "蜂房组",
  "icon": "complicated_bees:mellarium_base",
  "category": "complicated_bees:machines",
  "advancement": "complicated_bees:advanced_products",
  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "想必你已经攒足了养蜂经验，是时候给蜜蜂们找些更好的住处了。$(br2)蜂房组是工业级尺寸的蜂房，可在其中嵌入特殊模块，以让产出速度更上一层楼。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "蜂房组自身带有 1.25 倍的工作速度加成，可以用模块进一步增加。$(br2)需格外注意，蜂房组的$(l)顶层不接受除基础方块外的蜂房组方块$()。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "multiblock": {
        "pattern": [
          ["BBB","BBB","BBB"],
          ["###","###","###"],
          ["###","#0#","###"]
        ],
        "mapping": {
          "B": "complicated_bees:mellarium_base",
          "#": "#complicated_bees:multiblock/mellarium",
          "0": "#complicated_bees:multiblock/mellarium"
        }
      },
      "text": "不推荐跨区块边界放置，也不推荐两两相邻放置。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_panel",
      "recipe2": "complicated_bees:mellarium_base"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_frame_housing_1",
      "title": "框架槽",
      "text": "框架槽可插入框架，数量由其等级决定：基础框架槽最多 1 个，普通最多 2 个，大型 3 个。各框架效果连续乘算，收益逐个递减，乘算上限为 50000x。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_frame_housing_2",
      "recipe2": "complicated_bees:mellarium_frame_housing_3",
      "title": "框架槽"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_mutator",
      "title": "突变器",
      "text": "每次蜂后死亡时，消耗一份致突变剂，以增加其产出突变后代的概率。可用致催化剂列表见配方浏览器。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_temp_unit",
      "title": "温控单元",
      "text": "每个蜜蜂工作循环刻中，有概率消耗特定物品，以升高或降低蜂房组的温度。可用消耗品见配方浏览器。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_hydroregulator",
      "title": "湿度调节器",
      "text": "每个蜜蜂工作循环刻中，有概率消耗特定物品，以升高或降低蜂房组的湿度；同时有概率产出废弃物。具体见配方浏览器。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_rain_shield",
      "title": "雨屏",
      "text": "借助海洋之心的力量，为蜜蜂们遮风挡雨。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_energy_cell",
      "title": "能量单元",
      "text": "为耗能模块存储能量。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_skybox",
      "title": "天空盒",
      "text": "使用能量为蜜蜂模拟露天环境。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_temporal_simulator",
      "title": "时间模拟器",
      "text": "使用能量让蜜蜂保持清醒，工作不停歇。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "recipe": "complicated_bees:mellarium_output_hatch",
      "title": "输出仓",
      "text": "向相接的容器迅速输出。"
    }
  ]
}